The paper discusses the design of culture-aware robots, which involves aspects of robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), and systems and control (cs.SY). The use of fuzzy logic in the proposed framework also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG).
